<h2>You received a donation!</h2>
<p>Great news, {{organizerName}}! Your campaign just received a donation.</p>
<p class="amount">${{amountDollars}}</p>
<p><strong>Campaign:</strong> {{campaignTitle}}</p>
{{#unless isAnonymous}}
<p><strong>From:</strong> {{donorName}}</p>
{{else}}
<p><strong>From:</strong> Anonymous donor</p>
{{/unless}}
{{#if message}}
<p><strong>Message:</strong> "{{message}}"</p>
{{/if}}
<p><strong>Net amount (after fees):</strong> ${{netAmountDollars}}</p>
<a href="{{appUrl}}/dashboard/campaigns/{{campaignId}}" class="cta">View Campaign Dashboard</a>
<hr />
<p style="font-size:13px; color:#6b7280;">Funds are processed by Stripe and disbursed to your connected bank account on a rolling basis.</p>
